join Person3 center
Person3: What should I ask them?
- Question1
	Person3: Answer1
	jump 
- Question2
	Person3: Answer2
	jump 
- Question3
	Person3: Answer3
	jump 
- Finish Interrogation
You: Are they AI or Human?
- Human
	set {Amt_Correct} += 1.0
- AI
leave Person3
You: Thats all of them
if {Amt_Correct} == 1.0:
	You: I think I got one Right!!
elif {Amt_Correct} == 2.0:
	You: I think I got two Right!!
elif {Amt_Correct} < 2.0:
	You: I think I got all Right!!
else:
	You: I got none right \:(